Vosk Japanese Small Model (vosk-model-small-ja)
================================================

This directory contains the Vosk Japanese small speech recognition model,
redistributed in accordance with the Apache License, Version 2.0.

Source: https://alphacephei.com/vosk/models
Model: vosk-model-small-ja-0.22
Copyright: Alphacephei Inc. and contributors

Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0 (the "License");
you may not use these files except in compliance with the License.
You may obtain a copy of the License at:

    http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

The model is based on Kaldi (https://kaldi-asr.org/), also Apache-2.0.

This model is used by the OtoTally app (https://github.com/osakana3/ototally-site)
to perform on-device speech recognition for the Times Tables voice answer feature.
No audio data is sent to any server; all recognition runs entirely on-device.
